text:
Very Nice, Beautiful Scenery and Peaceful Environment far away from the City, with nature surroundings which let you feel like living in countryside. Love it...!
Looks almost like Condominium Design.
But there are toooooo many Children's Playgrounds already and located toooooo near block unit's window, which could be noisy for those staying at lower floor levels.
Best Design HDB Block, Build Between Punggol Jetty And Coney Island
